chunks.translated_text:
Heavenly spirits, earthly spirits, the Six Jia and Six Ding.
Wind Earl and Rain Master, the Five Thunder Divine Soldiers.
The Radiant Mother of Lightning, the Thunderbolt General—
follow the talisman in haste to strike down demonic essences.
Swiftly, swiftly, as the law commands!

**Talisman of the Great One’s Three Mountains and Wooden Lad Spirit**

In the east of Jade Pool, the pure yang streams its brilliance;
the sacred one of the Covenant’s Might is named Green Youth.
Hurl fire ten thousand leagues into the Kan and Zhen palaces,
valiant steeds swiftly gallop forth to Mount Tai Meng.
The primordial chaos was split open, piercing through Kongtong;
green waves lift the sky, turning toward the Gou Rong.
The secret decree of Azure Radiance commands and seals—
all talismanic orders descend from the imperial palace.

The Wooden Lad, mighty hero of the Great One’s Three Mountains,
supremely reveres the Mysterious Subtle, following with utmost devotion.
With a *xu* and *hu*, he drives thunder to rise from the earth’s veins;
thunderbolts shatter stone, and spring sources flow unobstructed.
From Kun to Xun’s gate, the Radiant Elder—
crystal streams and dense light rush toward Zhu Rong.
Four fierce steeds charge with bursting fire;
the great chariot ascends Mount Taihua amid the clouds.
Golden hammers and jade iron gleam with fiery bows;
heaven-shaking drums of *tao* resound with *dong-dong*.
The Heavenly Stem Great Sage descends with true wisdom;
the Divine Empyrean’s talismanic command shines with numinous clarity.
Striking ten thousand evils, leaving no trace behind—
I now, by command, summon the Thunder Duke.

To east and west, south and north, bursting fire gathers;
banners and pennants flutter down through the empty sky.
The Asura, after a day’s delay, returns to Sang Yong;
the envoy of Vaisravana, Tian Yuan Yong.
The Kun’s tail sways, stirring celestial paper talismans;
the Flame Thearch steams rain, amassing thick clouds.
In an instant, the Kan position swells with black qi;
the August Emperor’s radiance blazes, piercing both pupils.
Yan Bo shakes the peaks of Kunlun;
driving thunder and wielding lightning, he rides a fire dragon.
Flying sand and rolling stones fill the empty sky;
dark spirits overturn the sea, joining with Xuan Ming.
Feng Yi dances and howls the long wind;
the Weaving Maiden and Four Brothers lead the vanguard.
Ju Lou Ji Li chases the Azure Dragon;
Ding Xin Di Xi grasps the Emperor’s bell.
The Covenant’s Might envoy—frost congeals in winter;
the Jade Radiance Lad pounds ceaselessly.
Yaya Ze Shu roars to the vault of heaven;
Chun Ming Qi Mie burns the poisonous centipedes.
Huang Li wields his sword to slay the [missing character];
the Han minister, by command, inspects your person.

The weak waters of Penglai rise in merit at Xing Du;
the immortal retinue of Yingzhou returns with *ding-dang*.
When the Jade Bureau’s orders descend, none dare be idle;
all departments hold the summons, none disobey.
Heavenly thunder rumbles, clashing golden bells;
divine thunder’s mighty power shatters the canopy.
Dragon thunder shakes the sky with crimson fire;
water thunder drums the waves, filling the sea to its brim.
The Earth God commands the strike against demonic hordes;
the drought fiend of Li Yang is obliterated without trace.
The long crossbow of Yu Kang sweeps away rainbows;
the Six-One swiftly intercepts to ward off misfortune.
Crimson-haired, with giant wings and twin pupils—
thunder and lightning spew poison, driving the Five Dragons.
The Four Seas mist over, shrouded in layered yin;
following my Yu Step, numinous power descends.
The earth and sky tremble in haste—
beheading drought spirits and all demonic sects.
A single flash of fire turns ten thousand leagues red;
burning away evil demons, leaving no dust behind.
When the talismanic command arrives, rain flows freely;
thunder and lightning surge with *dong-dong* drums.
Driving the thunder hosts, black rain follows—
a single roar, and the Four Seas are veiled in mist.
Golden Radiance and Dui’s marsh fly in solemn harmony;
Kan initiates, Li aligns—commanding the Mysterious Clan.
Water patterns hasten change at Heaven’s Gate’s lofty gaze;
lightning flashes through the sky, scorching flames roar.
Gong Gong’s minister, Gong Bin, descends with halberds;
where the rain phalanx arrives, rivers surge in flood.
A great thunderclap shakes the seas in a ring;
the Lord Bright, the Primordial August, leads the vanguard.
Shang Yang calls out *wu*, her cloud-toppled hair unbound;
red chickens and purple geese overturn golden cages.
Flowing cinnabar and auspicious vapors rise in luxuriant tangle;
the Ninefold Heaven’s Gate hangs with crimson maples.
The Old Man of Mount Tai meets Feng Meng;
the Numinous One of Southern Marchmount Heng leads Chi Song.
The Western Hua’s Metal Heaven employs the Four Fiends;
Mount Heng’s Black Pottery startles Yu Gong.
The Central Yi’s Five Luminaries pay homage to Tian Song;
a hundred spirits descend from the sky, riding divine steeds.
*Duo Zhe Jiu Luo* slays flying insects;
the Ice Turtledove warms the stone den of A Xiong.
Holding the jade tablet, he extends years—Zhen Er Xiong;
Hao Meng’s yellow thorns cleave to the ancestral line.
Rong Xiong and Gui Yan flash like the Jiu Peng;
Si Quan Zi Zhen’s might commands Heaven’s Duke.
The Two Ancestors of the Abyssal Cavern return to the Emperor’s will;
the envoy Chi Fu traverses the sky with a transverse flute.
Heavenly demons block the path, yet none dare attack;
the lotus of Brocade River sings of Kongtong.
The Divine Empyrean examines human good and evil;
the Jade Tablet’s great command drives the thunder gods.
Beheading tigers and leopards, slaying fierce *rong*;
endless generals and officials, hearts heavy with care.
With single-minded devotion, bow and revere the Jade Countenance;
the myriad heavens and starry hosts align without error.
All phenomena belong to the Mysterious Mechanism’s clan;
the Water-Transporting Messenger comes and goes between.
Heaven’s marsh descends in long, flowing streams—
assisting my Daoist arts to flourish day by day.
Assisting me to rescue drought and transform the times into abundance;
assisting me to rescue drought, my merit and glory soar.
Ten thousand evils are struck down, their traces erased;
all things achieve completion, returning to the great refining.
Heaven’s glory is shared, merit boundless.

**Decree!** The Southern Pole’s Purple August Primordial Lady descends.
Swiftly, swiftly, as the Fire Command seizes!

**Further Decree and Incantation**

Great Thunder Duke of All Heavens,
thunderbolts shake the empty sky.
Three hundred thousand troops of blades and spears—
fiery radiance blazes in the Purple Grotto.
Dare any disobey?
The stern command brooks no delay.
Seize and deliver them beneath the Dipper’s Stem—
forever to become the pure, tranquil wind.
Swiftly, swiftly, as the law commands!

**Dispatch Incantation**

Hūm hūm, dōu shù, Brahmā-responding thunder roars and seizes.
By the True King’s solemn decree, the Jade Emperor’s edict is issued.
All spirits under heaven, heed the command of this altar—none may disobey.
Swiftly, swiftly, as the Divine Empyrean’s primordial descending oral decree and ordinance!

Burn incense, summon, and invoke:
From the Great Dao of Cavernous Mystery, the presiding master of the law, Flame Thearch Deng Heavenly Lord;
Radiant Flow of Hua-Yin’s Effulgence, Vermilion Heavenly Lord of the Great One;
Flying Light of the Fire Bell, Supreme Sage Heavenly Lord of the Great One;
Wooden Youth of the Great One, Supreme Sage Heavenly Lord;
The Three, Five, and Nine Yangs’ Fire Master Lü Divine Lord of Shaoyang;
The Eight Great Divine Lords—Cai, Jin, Su, Chen, Zhang, Jiang, Bi, and Cheng.

Fiery Flowing Metal Fire Bell, Great Immortal Xie of Fire;
Fire-Dwelling Earl Zhou Marshal;
Yin-Yang Thunder-Operating Yu and Ren, the Two Great Marshals;
Azure Fang and Iron Face, Heavenly Lord Liu;
Officers and generals of the Jade Slips and Sword-Tip Law of the Great One;
The inner and outer ramparts of the Cavernous Mystery, the left and right courts of the Nine Heavens, all affiliated thunder marshals and thunder soldiers;
Envoys of the Barbarian Thunders of the Five Directions;
All departments of perfected great spirits—
Each is invited to attend the altar and receive this commission.

The incantation states:
*Hūm □ dā □ dā □ □ dā □ □ dā □ □ dā □ dā kā □ □ xī yí tí □ lī dā □ □ jiè xì.*
As in the ordinance of the Primordial Cavernous Mystery Thunder Sovereign Emperor.
One qi, three repetitions.

Burn incense, summon, and invoke:
From the Great Dao of Pure Tenuity, the Western Terrace’s Commander-in-Chief, Wolf-Fang Valiant Officer Chen Marshal;
Vice General Shi Marshal;
The Nine Heavens’ Responsive Primordial Swift Ordinance, Numinous Flying Divine Talisman Envoy Zhang Messenger;
From the *Jade Pivot Scripture*’s thunderous and blazing law, the Five Great Heavenly Lords—Deng, Xin, Zhang, Xun, and Liu—
Hasten to the altar’s front to manifestly reveal karmic response.
Swiftly!

Burn incense, summon, and invoke:
From the Southern Culmen and Northern Heart’s Orthodox Law of the Three Luminaries, the talisman officers;
From the Dipper’s Numinous Writ and Heavenly Heart Law’s departments, the marshals, generals, officers, soldiers, and White Seizers;
From the Great Thunder Law, the Thunder Gate’s Left Demon-Quelling Envoy, Supervisor of the Southern Culmen’s Heavenly Pivot Court and General Administrator of the Thunder Bureau’s One Prefecture, Two Courts, and Three Offices, Marshal Gou;
The Thunder Gate’s Right Demon-Quelling Envoy, Director of the Northern Culmen’s Demon-Dispelling Court and Military Overseer of the Thunder Bureau, Marshal Bi;
The Thirty-Six Thunder Drum Valiant Warriors;
The Seventy-Two Examiners and Summoning Spirits;
The Four Great Envoys—Chen, Liu, Sun, and Zhang—
Hasten to the altar’s front to immediately manifest karmic response.

The incantation states:
*Oṃ.*

