hree revolutions, three layers of walls;
four revolutions, four layers of walls;
five revolutions, five layers of walls;
six revolutions, six layers of walls;
seven revolutions, seven layers of walls;
eight revolutions, eight layers of walls;
nine revolutions, nine layers of walls—
within the ninefold walls, summon the Heavenly Soldiers!
Solemnly invoke the Five Directions’ Ghost-Pursuing Generals to nail the ghosts without exception!
*Swiftly, swiftly, as the statutes command!*

*Merge forms.*"

chunks.translated_text:
**General Summons of the Myriad Spirits Talisman Secret**

Marshal Ban, Grand Master for Summoning Perfections and Calling Spirits Cui Ziwen of the Primordial Beginning’s Hall, Dispatcher of the Three Realms’ Merit Officers, Golden Watchtower’s Upper Assistant Historian Gui Zhang—
These two spirits, clad in vermilion robes with voluminous sleeves, appear in the guise of Dragon-Tiger Lords, riding upon purple clouds. One bears the tally, the other holds the Supreme Thearch’s true talisman.

**General Summons of the Two Great Marshals Luo Hui and Jing Yao—**
The two marshals, clad in vermilion robes with voluminous sleeves, bear banners and tallies, riding upon purple clouds.

**Summoning Incantation**
Vast and formless, the primordial abyss swells;
The Northern Sea surges, the Eastern Lake teems.
From the *zi* hour, radiance blazes forth;
At noon, brilliance burns with scorching flame.
At noon, the Azure Thearch convenes the spirits;
At *mao*, the White Thearch attends the souls.
From *chen* to *bai*, the Vermilion Thearch nurtures *qi*;
At noon, the Black Thearch governs the blood.
The Yellow Thearch presides at the center;
At *shen*, the myriad spirits transcend none.
With the jade mudra, perform one, five, three transformations—
Leftward, three revolutions disperse the ten thousand beings.
Rightward, three revolutions gather the wind to unite the spirits;
*Chou*, *yin*, *mao*, *chen*—silent resonance pervades.
*Si*, *wu*, *wei*, *shen*—only the true respond;
All *xu*-hour rebels dare not stir.
At *hai*, tranquility governs and orders;
*Zi* and *chou* summon the spirits by the law.
The central line ascends to *li* fire to summon *qi* by spirit;
Beneath *li*, the central line ascends again to *li*, congealing it naturally.
The middle finger presses the base of the thumb, circulating through heaven and earth;
Revolving through the twelve palaces, the celestial heart issues its command.
The myriad spirits reverently heed—
Form the Dipper mudra, once for Rāhu’s baleful force.
Middle above: two for Greedy Wolf’s decree;
Middle center: three for Ketu’s seizure.

**Baleful Script**
General Summons Talisman

